<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="logo-row">
    <div class="logo-badge pt">PURE TECHNOLOGY</div>
    <div class="x-mark">&times;</div>
    <div class="logo-badge rootcode">ROOTCODE</div>
  </div>
  <p class="prepared-for">Prepared exclusively for <strong>Alagan Mahalingam, CEO</strong></p>
  <h1>You Built a World-Class Engineering Company.<br>Now <span>Multiply It.</span></h1>
  <p class="header-sub">This page was researched, written, and deployed by one person working with one AI partner. That''s PureBrain in action.</p>

</div>

<!-- STAT BAR -->
<div class="stat-bar">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">100+</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Engineers and Growing</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">3</div>
    <div class="stat-label">EU Governments Served</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">ISO</div>
    <div class="stat-label">9001 + 27001 Certified</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">APICTA</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Award Winner</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 1: WE DID OUR HOMEWORK -->
<div class="section-title">We Did Our Homework</div>
<div class="research-grid">
  <div class="research-card">
    <h4>What Rootcode Has Built</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Estonia''s national AI model training platform for government agencies</li>
      <li>Three divisions: Rootcode Labs (engineering), Rootcode AI (intelligence), and Rootcode Studio (design)</li>
      <li>Enterprise clients including the United Nations, Kendrion, and BRP Systems</li>
      <li>ISO 9001 and ISO 27001 certified, meeting the strictest compliance requirements in European procurement</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="research-card">
    <h4>Where Rootcode Is Headed</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Ambitious growth plans, scaling the team significantly over the next decade</li>
      <li>Headquartered in Sri Lanka with offices in Estonia and the USA, building a world-class hub</li>
      <li>Alagan''s vision: AI as the backbone of citizen engagement for governments worldwide</li>
      <li>Rootcode Foundation investing in 1,000+ students, building the pipeline for the next generation</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="research-card full-width">
    <h4>The Real Challenge</h4>
    <p>Rootcode is not a typical outsourcing company. You are a product-minded engineering firm that wins contracts other companies cannot touch. Estonia chose you over European competitors. The United Nations trusts you with critical systems. That quality is exactly what makes ambitious growth so dangerous: every company that has scaled rapidly has faced the same question. How do you multiply headcount without diluting the standard that earned those contracts? The companies that solve this become institutions. The ones that do not become commodities.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2: THREE VALUE PROPOSITIONS -->
<div class="section-title">Three Ways PureBrain Changes the Equation</div>
<div class="value-props">

  <!-- VALUE PROP 1 -->
  <div class="value-prop">
    <div class="vp-header">
      <div>
        <div class="vp-name">Every Engineer Gets a Partner That Never Forgets</div>
        <div class="vp-sub">Persistent AI that compounds knowledge about your codebase, your clients, and your standards</div>
      </div>
      <span class="vp-number">Value 01</span>
    </div>
    <div class="vp-body">
      <ul>
        <li class="highlight">Most AI tools reset every conversation. PureBrain does not. Each developer''s AI partner accumulates context over weeks and months, learning Rootcode''s architecture patterns, coding standards, and client-specific requirements.</li>
        <li>At 100+ engineers, that''s 100+ AI partners working alongside your team. As you grow, so does the AI layer. Each one retaining everything it''s learned.</li>
        <li>Code reviews that know your conventions. Documentation that writes itself in your voice. Debugging that remembers the last three times a similar issue appeared and what fixed it.</li>
        <li>The difference between a chatbot and a partner is memory. PureBrain remembers.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="ref">Reference: Internal deployment. John Smith (Pure Technology VP Sales) uses PureBrain with his AI partner Anchor daily. One person producing the research output of a team. This page is one example of that output.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VALUE PROP 2 -->
  <div class="value-prop">
    <div class="vp-header">
      <div>
        <div class="vp-name">Win Government Tenders at 5x the Speed</div>
        <div class="vp-sub">AI-powered proposals that maintain Rootcode precision with a fraction of the manual effort</div>
      </div>
      <span class="vp-number">Value 02</span>
    </div>
    <div class="vp-body">
      <ul>
        <li class="highlight">Government RFPs are documentation marathons. Compliance matrices, technical responses, past performance references, all written to exacting standards. PureBrain drafts these using your own winning submissions as the baseline.</li>
        <li>Estonia was the breakthrough. The question is how many Estonias you''re missing because your team can only respond to so many RFPs at a time.</li>
        <li>PureBrain automatically maps your ISO certifications, past contract performance, and technical capabilities to new RFP requirements, flagging gaps before submission.</li>
        <li>Every proposal maintains the rigour that won Estonia. Just delivered in days instead of weeks.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VALUE PROP 3 -->
  <div class="value-prop">
    <div class="vp-header">
      <div>
        <div class="vp-name">Scale Without Losing What Made You Special</div>
        <div class="vp-sub">Institutional knowledge that travels with the company, not locked in anyone''s head</div>
      </div>
      <span class="vp-number">Value 03</span>
    </div>
    <div class="vp-body">
      <ul>
        <li class="highlight">The hardest part of ambitious growth is not hiring, it''s preserving the knowledge, the standards, and the culture that won Estonia and the UN. Every fast-growing company loses institutional memory. PureBrain is how you keep it.</li>
        <li>Senior engineers'' expertise gets captured and distributed, so when someone leaves, their knowledge does not leave with them.</li>
        <li>New hires onboard faster because the AI already knows your processes, your patterns, and your client expectations. Day-one productivity instead of month-three ramp-up.</li>
        <li>Alagan''s foundation work, investing in 1,000+ students, shows Rootcode believes in developing people. PureBrain is the technology layer that makes that philosophy scale across the entire organisation.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 3: LIVING PROOF -->
<div class="section-title">You''re Looking at the Proof</div>
<div class="proof-box">
  <h3>This Page Is a PureBrain Deliverable</h3>
  <p class="proof-subtitle">Not a mockup. Not a demo. This is real output from a real PureBrain deployment, running right now.</p>
  <div class="proof-grid">
    <div class="proof-item">
      <span class="proof-icon">&#128269;</span>
      <div class="proof-label">Research</div>
      <div class="proof-desc">Anchor analysed Rootcode''s public profile, Alagan''s interviews, your Estonia government work, Foundation initiatives, ISO certifications, and growth trajectory.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="proof-item">
      <span class="proof-icon">&#9997;</span>
      <div class="proof-label">Writing</div>
      <div class="proof-desc">Every word on this page was drafted by Anchor, reviewed by John, and refined together. One human, one AI, iterating until it''s right.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="proof-item">
      <span class="proof-icon">&#128640;</span>
      <div class="proof-label">Deployment</div>
      <div class="proof-desc">Page designed, built, password-protected, and deployed to a live URL. All within a single working session.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="proof-narrative">
    <strong>How it happened:</strong> John Smith asked Anchor to prepare a tailored overview for Rootcode. Anchor researched your company, identified the three value propositions most relevant to your growth stage, wrote the page, built the design, and deployed it. John reviewed, gave feedback, and Anchor revised. The entire process, from "let''s build this" to the page you''re reading now, took one session. No agency, no design contractor, no copywriter. One person working alongside one persistent AI partner that already knows Pure Technology''s voice, positioning, and sales process from months of daily collaboration. <strong>That''s what compounding intelligence looks like in practice.</strong>
  </div>
  <p class="proof-cta">Now imagine every one of your engineers working this way.</p>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="cta-box">
