  <p>If any of this is relevant to where Rootcode is headed, we''d welcome the conversation. No pitch, no pressure, just a genuine exchange about what''s possible.</p>
  <div class="cta-contacts">
    <div class="cta-contact">
      <strong>John Smith</strong>
      VP Sales, Pure Technology<br>
      jsmith@puretechnology.nyc
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

